org.nd4j.evaluation

Interface IEvaluation<T extends IEvaluation>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IEvaluation<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseEvaluation, BaseEvaluation, CustomEvaluation, Evaluation, Evaluation, EvaluationBinary, EvaluationBinary, EvaluationCalibration, EvaluationCalibration, RegressionEvaluation, RegressionEvaluation, ROC, ROC, ROCBinary, ROCBinary, ROCMultiClass, ROCMultiClass

    public interface IEvaluation<T extends IEvaluation>
extends Serializable
    A general purpose interface for evaluating neural networks - methods are shared by implemetations such as Evaluation, RegressionEvaluation, ROC, ROCMultiClass
    Author:
    Alex Black
